  "title": "Full Stack Developer",
  "description": "<p><strong>About the Role</strong><br>\nWe are looking for a dedicated and talented Full Stack Developer with strong expertise in React.js, Node.js, and PHP to help develop and maintain scalable, high-performing web solutions. If you enjoy full-stack development and solving practical business challenges with clean and efficient code, we’d like to get in touch with you.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Create responsive and engaging user interfaces using React.js (with Hooks, Redux, and Context API)</li>\n  <li>Develop and maintain backend logic and REST APIs using Node.js, Express, and PHP</li>\n  <li>Design, implement, and manage database schemas and queries using MongoDB, PostgreSQL, and MySQL</li>\n  <li>Integrate external APIs and third-party services to enhance system capabilities</li>\n  <li>Ensure system performance, responsiveness, and scalability for production environments</li>\n  <li>Work closely with designers, product owners, and fellow developers within an agile development team</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>At least 4 years of practical experience in React.js, Node.js, and PHP development</li>\n  <li>Strong knowledge of JavaScript/TypeScript with familiarity in modern software development practices</li>\n  <li>Good grasp of Express.js, JWT-based authentication methods, and API design principles</li>\n  <li>Proficient with Git for source control and experienced with CI/CD tools and workflows</li>\n  <li>Comfortable using Docker for containerized application development and deployment</li>\n  <li>Experience in Python (using frameworks like Flask or Django)</li>\n  <li>Familiarity with Flutter for developing mobile applications</li>\n  <li>Exposure to AWS or other cloud computing platforms</li>\n</ul>",
